y 2007 \n|-\n| 32 || 32 || Lugga's New Job || James breaks down, causing Mamma Mia to ask Lugga to drive her around, but when the pair have fun together, the out-of-action chauffeur begins to get jealous. ||4 July 2007 \n|-\n| 33 || 33 || Silver Hatch Fun Run || Big Chris is undecided about taking part in a fun run, so Roary and Plugga try to make sure he trains for it without realizing. ||5 July 2007 \n|-\n| 34 || 34 || Silver Hatch Heroes || A film director visits Silver Hatch to record his new movie. ||6 July 2007 \n|-\n|}\n\n===Season 2 (2008)===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Overall !! Episode !! Title !! Description !! Airdate\n|-\n| 35 || 01 || Nick Solves the Case || Nick solves the case of the missing biofuel. ||10 July 2007\n|-\n| 36 || 02 || Dragga's Last Day || The little car worries that Dragga is to be taken to the scrapheap! ||11 July 2007\n|-\n| 37 || 03 || Out of Juice || Big Chris takes delivery of special rainwater to make the cars run more smoothly. ||12 July 2007\n|-\n| 38 || 04 || Roary's Wake Up Call || Farmer Green has problems getting up in the morning, so Roary finds a way to help. ||14 July 2007\n|-\n| 39 || 05 || Big Chris Says Sorry || Big Chris thinks Marsha is cross with him after he corrects a mistake made by Mrs. Carburettor. ||17 July 2007\n|-\n| 40 || 06 || Maxi's New Engine || Maxi's engine needs to be rebuilt. ||19 July 2007\n|-\n| 41 || 07 || A Busy Day for Big Chris || Big Chris struggles to find time to relax, because every time he sits down, someone at Silver Hatch race track wants his help. ||20 July 2007\n|-\n| 42 || 08 || Tin Top Gets Scared || Furz the rabbit decides to play a mischievous trick on Tin Top. ||21 July 2007\n|-\n| 43 || 09 || Roary Loses A Friend || Big Chris accidentally throws away Roary's lucky teddy, and sets out to retrieve it before it reaches the garbage dump. ||22 July 2007\n|-\n| 44 || 10 || Spooky Forest || Maxi tricks the friends into thinking the forest is haunted. ||24 July 2007\n|-\n| 45 || 11 || FB in the Fast Lane || Trucksy the flatbed truck competes against Maxi at the racetrack - with disastrous results! ||25 July 2007\n|-\n| 46 || 12 || Roary Goes Back to School || Roary heads back to school to brush up on his safety skills. ||26 July 2007\n|-\n| 47 || 13 || The Rabbit That Yelled Stop || Furz challenges Roary to take part in a race. ||28 July 2007\n|-\n| 48 || 14 || Zizzy Gets Fired Up || Silver Hatch suffers a fuel crisis, so everyone relies on solar-powered Zizzy! ||29 July 2007\n|-\n| 49 || 15 || Stars 'n' Cars || Big Chris is invited to sing karaoke on TV. ||30 July 2007\n|-\n| 50 || 16 || Crash Test Roary || Roary is nervous about racing after crashing into a tree while racing against Maxi. ||31 July 2007\n|-\n| 51 || 17 || Roary Sees Red || Zizzy gets stuck in the mud during a rainstorm while helping Farmer Green and FB with their annual hay harvest. ||1 September 2007\n|-\n| 52 || 18 || Rusty Takes a Trip || The cheerful racing car and his friends plan a surprise for Rusty. ||3 September 2007\n|-\n| 53 || 19 || Roary Cleans Up His Act || The colourful racing car tackles a water shortage at Silver Hatch race track to make sure the gang are ready for an important photo shoot! ||5 September 2007\n|-\n| 54 || 20 || Green-Eyed Roary || Maxi chooses Zizzy as his training partner, making Roary jealous. ||7 September 2007\n|-\n| 55 || 21 || Big Chris Forgets || Marsha celebrates her birthday, but Big Chris forgets all about the occasion! ||9 September 2007\n|-\n| 56 || 22 || Big Chris Babysits || The mechanic looks after Roary and Zizzy, but it seems he's the one who needs babysitting! ||10 September 2007\n|-\n| 57 || 23 || Roary and Nigel || Roary makes friends with Nigel the crab. ||14 September 2007\n|-\n| 58 || 24 || Roary Gets It Wrong || Farmer Green asks Roary the little car to deliver parcels around the track! ||15 September 2007\n|-\n| 59 || 25 || A Computer Calamity || Mr. Carburettor announces he wants to move with the times and be more 